a card is a thing
a card has a direction as either up or down

my-card = a new card with direction = down

to turn a card face up
	set its direction to up
to turn a card face down
	set its direction to down

turn my-card face up
expect the direction of my-card to be up

get my-card
turn it face up

to start the game
start the game

to flip a card over
	start the game

to turn a card over: 
	start the game
	if the direction of the card is up
		set the direction of it to down
	otherwise
		turn it face up		// TODO: why doesn't this work?